Summary: Did not see object during photography. Saw it the next day while reviewing photos.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking a photo of Agua Prieta Mexico on May 16, 2013, from "D" Hill in Douglas, Ariz., but didn't notice anything unusual until the next day while reviewing photos. Even after zooming in on the area in question, I can't identify the object. The photo has not been edited. I have never seen a UFO and I am a skeptic...with an open mind.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Agua Prieta
This sighting has never been favorited.
